{"tid":913499,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"《任天堂實驗室》系列確定推出中文版 首波《組合套裝》2019 年 1 月上市","createTime":"2018-11-23T12:37:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-25T13:41:34.000Z","uid":38191,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"184525fa72bea0681f401a138b2acd795a9f2bce","tid":913499,"uid":38191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T12:37:27.000Z","msg":"任天堂今（23）日宣布，Nintendo Switch 創意紙板玩具《任天堂實驗室（Nintendo Labo）》系列將在台推出中文版，首波《任天堂實驗室 Toy-Con 01: 組合套裝》預定 2019 年 1 月推出。<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/09/d7965c69e354ecbbb9af452f121323p5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F09%2Fd7965c69e354ecbbb9af452f121323p5.JPG&h=52c27ee3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n　《任天堂實驗室》是把零件紙板砌成的「Toy-Con」與 Nintendo Switch 的「Joy-Con」組裝在一起玩的遊戲，至今從未有過的新玩法。製作時可以了解內部構造，探索新發現，發掘新玩法的同時，享受的樂趣也跟著豐富起來。這樣的「製作、遊玩、探索」以全新概念為基礎開發出的遊玩發明組合，在遊玩過程中也許不知不覺變成了遊戲發明家。<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/10/36e2f18313cdf53a6d90be5a201323q5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F10%2F36e2f18313cdf53a6d90be5a201323q5.JPG&h=160def93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f3802c4a38b1f32cd11bae231121079b7c4a212","tid":913499,"uid":29080,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T12:38:27.000Z","msg":"製造垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb3dd39d7d42647bb16c32ed7722a9d6856e9d17","tid":913499,"uid":12034,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T12:39:43.000Z","msg":"紙皮出左真係有人玩?"},{"pid":"6e5fe6077b2c4e182aaae1ed89c9fff13cde4890","tid":913499,"uid":36509,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"fb3dd39d7d42647bb16c32ed7